*
* This script tests the batch aspect of the test scripting facility.
*
* Invocation when running z390 under Windows/DOS:
* SET myscript=rt\rt\BATCHZ.RT
* bat\asmlg demo\HELLO test(myscript)
*
* Invocation when running Linux/*ux:
* export myscript=rt/rt/BATCHZ.RT
* bash/asmlg demo/HELLO "test(myscript)"
*
* Expected behavior:
* the psw and t5 commands should be executed normally
* then, upon reaching the z command the program should terminate normally.
psw
t5
z
